  "text": "Weighed samples of drug-loaded nanoparticles (10 mg) were dissolved in 10 ml of dichloromethane under sonication for 1 h. The samples were filtered through a membrane filter and analysed spectrophotometrically at 248 nm using a UV/Vis spectrophotometer (Shimadzu 1800). The percent drug loading and EE were determined using the below Eqns. All analyses were carried out in triplicate [CITATION_1] . % drug loading = mass of drug in nanoparticles/mass of nanoparticles recovered×100; % EE = mass of drug in nanoparticles/ mass of drug used in preparation×100.",
